sentences: Bang Hyun-sung (Korean: 방현성; Hanja: 方縣成; born June 16, 1991), professionally known as Ryan Bang, is a South Korean host, singer, comedian, actor and television personality in the Philippines.
He rose to fame in the Philippines when he joined the reality show Pinoy Big Brother: Teen Clash 2010, where he finished as a runner-up.
He hosted his first show, 3ow Powhz!, which aired from late 2010 until early 2011 on Studio 23.
